## ğŸ› ï¸ Development

1. Clone the repository
2. Create a virtual environment:

```
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Linux/Mac
venv\Scripts\activate     # Windows
```

3. Install dependencies:

```
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

4. Run tests:

```
pytest
```

